  "prompt": "Who all are having there IIM Indore IPM interview on 10th June in Delhi?",
  "response": "To get information on who is scheduled for the IIM Indore IPM interview on June 10th in Delhi, you would typically need to do the following:\n\n1. **Check Your Email:** If you have applied for the program, you should have received an email with your interview schedule.\n2. **Official Website:** Sometimes, institutes post general information about interview dates and locations on their official websites.\n3. **Candidate Groups:** Joining candidate forums or groups on social media platforms like LinkedIn or WhatsApp might help you connect with other applicants who could share their interview schedules.\n\nIf you are a candidate and need specific information, I recommend checking the aforementioned resources or directly contacting the admissions office of IIM Indore for precise details about your interview schedule.",
